{
  "chapter": 40,
  "chapter_summary": "本章竹台上，钱卓故意嘲弄仇恕与慕容惜生同进同退，引发二人误会与真情冲突。钱卓暗令断指大汉以暗器偷袭，慕容舍身救仇恕，丐帮群豪与断指大汉随即血战。仇恕、凌龙逼钱卓止战，双方一度收手，却又被潜伏的三名麻衣乞丐挑拨复燃。仇恕识破其阴谋，指出他们既恨丐帮也与灵蛇毛臬不和，钱卓遂扑向三人查明真相。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "钱卓",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "久闻大名，今日当真幸会得很！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "text": "我看你却不幸得很！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "钱卓",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "这位姑娘是谁？在下眼疏的很！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "text": "你管我是谁！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "钱卓",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "在下只是看到姑娘与仇公子同进同退，宛如一体，是以忍不住问上一问，姑娘如不愿说……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "text": "谁和他宛如一体，你说话放清楚些！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "钱卓",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "妙极妙极……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "text": "妙什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "你要做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "我要走了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "我绝不走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "这里的人我都不认得，这里的事与我毫无干涉，无论你愿不愿去，我却是必定要走的了！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "你要走便走好了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "凌龙",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "仇公子，这究竟是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "钱卓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妙极妙极……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "你当真不走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "死也不走！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_shen_ce_da_han",
      "text": "你过来。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_ce_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "身侧大汉",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "姑娘有何吩咐？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_shen_ce_da_han",
      "text": "再走近一些。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_ce_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "身侧大汉",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "姑娘——",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_ce_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "身侧大汉",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "姑娘这是做什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "你放不放手？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "你砍去我的手好了，何必作贱自己？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "我偏要作贱自己，我死了也和你无关。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "钱卓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "出手。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "你到底要我怎么样，你说呀……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "你不要管我……不要管我……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "你为什么要这样折磨我？你要砍就砍我的好了。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "我何尝折磨你，是你……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "我不好，你杀了我好了。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "伏下去！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "凌龙",
      "listener": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "text": "无耻，匹夫！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gai_bang_hu_he_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "丐帮呼喝弟子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "帮主俱已动手，我们还站在这作甚？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "谢谢……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "谢什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_xia_gai_bang_hao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "台下丐帮豪士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "下来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_yi_ge_gai_bang_hao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "另一个丐帮豪士",
      "listener": "char_tai_xia_gai_bang_hao_shi",
      "text": "干得好！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "钱卓",
      "listener": "char_ling_yi_ge_gai_bang_hao_shi",
      "text": "上来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "钱卓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们要想以三敌一，也只管动手便是。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "凌龙",
      "listener": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "text": "你配？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_ling_long",
      "text": "凌帮主且慢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "凌龙",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "还和他多什么话，先宰了他再说！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_ling_long",
      "text": "他一条性命能值几何，又何苦教丐帮的弟兄，白白赔上许多条无辜的性命，凌帮主说是么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "text": "你若想留下一命，便快叫他们住手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "钱卓",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "我为何要叫他们住手？看看别人流血，岂非人生一乐？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "text": "你自己的性命难道也不要了？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "钱卓",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "我若下令住手，你能否保证我等安全撤退？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "text": "他不保证，我也保证！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "钱卓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此刻双方伤残已重，人人都已凶性大发，我即使下令住手，他们也未必能听从我的话了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "text": "如此说来，该怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "钱卓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死光为止！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "凌龙",
      "listener": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "text": "你我一齐喝令住手如何？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "钱卓",
      "listener": "char_ling_long",
      "text": "你若要试上一试，我也未尝不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "凌龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "丐帮弟子住手！丐帮弟子住手！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "钱卓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弟兄们一齐住手！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "凌龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "丐帮弟子住手！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "再不住手，我真要……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gai_bang_fu_chou_di_zi_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丐帮复仇弟子一",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弟兄们已死了这么多，我们活着的人，若不替他复仇雪恨，对得起他们，对得起良心么？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gai_bang_fu_chou_di_zi_er",
      "speaker_name": "丐帮复仇弟子二",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀呀，杀光了他们，为死去的弟兄复仇！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "凌龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么人乱叫？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_zhi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "断指大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不守信的匹夫，咱们拼了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shou_chuang_gai_bang_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "受创丐帮弟子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弟兄们，复仇……",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "钱卓",
      "listener": "char_ling_long",
      "text": "丐帮首先违约，怪不得我了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "凌龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "违命之人，定当重办！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
